### Room API Test

### 방 생성 (POST /rooms)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/rooms
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roomName": "함께하는 쇼핑",
  "targetBudget": 500000,
  "syncMode": "FOLLOW",
  "roomMeta": {
    "shoppingPurpose": "친구들과 함께하는 겨울 쇼핑",
    "interestCategories": ["패션", "전자제품", "가구"],
    "headcount": 4,
    "budgetMin": 100000
  }
}

###

###

### 방 조회 - ID로 조회 (GET /rooms/{roomId})
GET http://localhost:8080/api/rooms/1

###

### 방 조회 - 초대 코드로 조회 (GET /rooms/code/{roomCode})
GET http://localhost:8080/api/rooms/code/426302D1

###

### 방 입장
POST http://localhost:8080/api/rooms/join
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roomCode": "426302D1",
  "nickname": "게스트2"
}

###

### 참여자 목록 조회 (GET /rooms/{roomId}/members)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/rooms/4/members

###

### 방 나가기 (DELETE /rooms/{roomId}/members/{memberId})
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/rooms/4/members/17

###

### 동기화 모드 변경 (PATCH /rooms/{roomId}/sync-mode) - 호스트만 가능
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/rooms/4/sync-mode
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "syncMode": "FREE"
}

###

### 호스트 URL 업데이트 (PATCH /rooms/{roomId}/host-url) - FOLLOW 모드
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/rooms/5/host-url
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "currentUrl": "https://example.com"
}

###

### 참여자 상태 업데이트 (PATCH /rooms/{roomId}/members/{memberId})
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/rooms/4/members/17
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isCameraOn": true
}

###

### 방 종료 (POST /rooms/{roomId}/close) - 호스트만 가능
POST http://localhost:8080/api/rooms/4/close

###
